    by The Freddie Nelson Show
    published on 2014-09-21T16:38:27Z










    Yo listener. Join me as I run through the many factors you need to consider when choosing between the iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus. I look at the pros and cons of each which will help you decide which is best for you.

I also give my view in the outline launch of the Apple Watch. happening in 2015.

Will the Apple Watch take over the smart phone in the future as the wearable device we will all use?
